**DevCapsule, a Manchester based VPS provider**

**Our platform consists of a custom built control panel and a 3 step server deployment process. It features -**
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Within 30 second deployments – from Click to Online in seconds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;noVNC Console direct to your server&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detailed Usage Graphs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hourly Billing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One-click reinstalls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom ISO’s – simply provide a URL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SSH Keys – add a public key and authenticate with your server as soon as it’s deployed (Added support for ssh-ed25519)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DNS Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BGP Sessions (Fully automated)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backups - Backup directly to your AWS S3 Buckets, SFTP or use our AWS S3 Managed storage. Automatic Scheduling and one-click restores.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Snapshots - Create snapshots of VM's allowing fast deployments of new applications or to scale your stack!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manchester, UK | Amsterdam, NL| Los Angeles, USA (LAX Currently Out of Stock)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

**We’ve got a wide variety of plans available to meet your needs our plans start at -**
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tiny&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 vCPU&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;512MB RAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10GB 100% SSD Storage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;500GB Transfer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
[For just £2.00 per month or £0.003 per hour ](https://www.devcapsule.com/pricing/?utm_source=LET&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=June)&lt;br&gt;
($2.65/pcm at current USD/GBP conversion)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Small&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 vCPU&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1024MB RAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;15GB 100% SSD Storage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1000GB Transfer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
[For just £4.00 per month or £0.005 per hour ](https://www.devcapsule.com/pricing/?utm_source=LET&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=June)&lt;br&gt;
($5.31/pcm at current USD/GBP conversion)

[To deploy or see our other plans signup here](https://www.devcapsule.com/pricing/?utm_source=LET&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=June)

We accept PayPal, Credit/Debit Card (Stripe) and Bitcoin as a payment method.

If you have any questions, please feel free to comment or submit a ticket

You can also join DevCapsule on [Discord](https://discord.gg/xDgs3jy).

Happy Deploying!
